177 A.3d 126 JOSE CONTRERAS MORALES, BY AND THROUGH HIS GUARDIAN AD LITEM, LILIANA MORALES FERNANDEZ, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. SUSSEX COUNTY COMMUNITY COLLEGE AND SOPHIE DUTKOWSKI, DEFENDANTS-RESPONDENTS, AND CARROLL SERVICES, INC., DEFENDANT, AND FIDEL RODRIGUEZ AND CAMPBELL'S SMALL ENGINE SALES AND SERVICE, INC., DEFENDANTS.

C-433 September Term 2017

080107 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000305-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
